snippet.title: Live: Lala Shades Randall, Girardi Laptop Seized, + Ramona vs. Kenya on RHUGT
snippet.description:
Re-broadcast of Friday night's IG Live, breaking down the biggest weekend headlines. 

We tackle: 
- Lala Kent's bRand new merch, shading Randall Emmett 
- Girardi Keese CFO has agreed to cooperate with the bankruptcy investigation 
- Kathy Hilton Speaks out re: RHOBH 
- Ramona vs. Kenya feud on Real Housewives Ultimate Girls Trip (Episode 5 Spoilers) 
- Scheana Shay announces she wants another baby (via surrogate)
